  "data_shape_notes": [
    "get_audience_report: `fake_follower_pct` = suspicious/bot followers; `mass_follower_pct` = real but low-value mass-following accounts. They are DISTINCT dimensions — never sum or conflate them.",
    "search_creators / get_creator_profile: every creator carries a canonical `creatorland_url` deep link; the MCP NEVER returns creator contact info (email/phone/DM) — the contact route is Creatorland itself.",
    "query_market_intelligence: aggregates carry a `provenance` string and clear a minimum-N privacy floor; a below-floor slice returns a SUCCESSFUL `refused` envelope (no data), never a JSON-RPC error.",
    "match_creators is free (0 credits); enrich_matches bills dynamically (3 credits per FUNDED match), so its fixed CREDIT_WEIGHTS entry is 0 — the real charge is recorded per-run, not from the static weight.",
    "brand affiliations describe DEAL ACTIVITY (a creator has worked with a brand category), never INTENT or a current/exclusive relationship."
  ]
